{
  "video_id": "NWUFjb8w9Ps",
  "title": "Math class needs a makeover | Dan Meyer",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "Can I ask you to please recall a time"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "when you really loved something --"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 22260.0,
      "text": "a movie, an album, a song or a book --"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "and you recommended it wholeheartedly"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "to someone you also really liked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "and you anticipated that reaction, you waited for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "and it came back, and the person hated it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "So, by way of introduction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "that is the exact same state"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "in which I spent every working day of the last six years. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "I teach high school math."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "I sell a product to a market"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "that doesn&#39;t want it, but is forced by law to buy it."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "I mean, it&#39;s just a losing proposition."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s a useful stereotype about students that I see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "a useful stereotype about you all."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "I could give you guys"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "an algebra-two final exam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "and I would expect no higher"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "than a 25 percent pass rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 66259.0,
      "text": "And both of these facts say less about you or my students"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "than they do about what we call math education"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "in the U.S. today."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "To start with, I&#39;d like to break math down into two categories."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "One is computation; this is the stuff you&#39;ve forgotten."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "For example, factoring quadratics with"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "leading coefficients greater than one."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "This stuff is also really easy to relearn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "provided you have a really strong grounding"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "in reasoning. Math reasoning --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll call it the application"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "of math processes to the world around us --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "this is hard to teach."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "This is what we would love students to retain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "even if they don&#39;t go into mathematical fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "This is also something that, the way we teach it in the U.S."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "all but ensures they won&#39;t retain it."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;d like to talk about why that is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "why that&#39;s such a calamity for society, what we can do about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "and, to close with, why this is an amazing time"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "to be a math teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "So first, five symptoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;re doing math reasoning wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "in your classroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "One is a lack of initiative; your students don&#39;t self-start."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "You finish your lecture block"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "and immediately you have five hands going up"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "asking you to re-explain the entire thing at their desks."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "Students lack perseverance."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "They lack retention; you find yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "re-explaining concepts three months later, wholesale."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an aversion to word problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "which describes 99 percent of my students."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "And then the other one percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "is eagerly looking for the formula"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "to apply in that situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "This is really destructive."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "David Milch, creator of \"Deadwood\" and other amazing TV shows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "has a really good description for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "He swore off creating"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "contemporary drama,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "shows set in the present day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "because he saw that when people fill their mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "with four hours a day of, for example, \"Two and a Half Men,\" no disrespect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "it shapes the neural pathways, he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 164260.0,
      "text": "in such a way that they expect simple problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 164260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "He called it, \"an impatience with irresolution.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re impatient with things that don&#39;t resolve quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "You expect sitcom-sized problems that wrap up in 22 minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "three commercial breaks and a laugh track."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll put it to all of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "what you already know, that no problem worth solving is that simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "I am very concerned about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;m going to retire in a world that my students will run."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 187260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m doing bad things"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "to my own future and well-being"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "when I teach this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m here to tell you that the way our textbooks -- particularly"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "mass-adopted textbooks -- teach math reasoning"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "and patient problem solving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s functionally equivalent to turning on \"Two and a Half Men\" and calling it a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "In all seriousness. Here&#39;s an example from a physics textbook."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "It applies equally to math."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "Notice, first of all here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "that you have exactly three pieces of information there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "each of which will figure into a formula"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "somewhere, eventually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "which the student will then compute."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "I believe in real life."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "And ask yourself, what problem have you solved, ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "that was worth solving"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "where you knew all of the given information in advance;"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "where you didn&#39;t have a surplus of information and you had to filter it out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "or you didn&#39;t have sufficient information"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "and had to go find some."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure we all agree that no problem worth solving is like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "And the textbook, I think, knows how it&#39;s hamstringing students"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "because, watch this, this is the practice problem set."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "When it comes time to do the actual problem set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "we have problems like this right here"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;re just swapping out numbers and tweaking the context a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "And if the student still doesn&#39;t recognize the stamp this was molded from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "it helpfully explains to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "what sample problem you can return to to find the formula."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "You could literally, I mean this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "pass this particular unit without knowing any physics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "just knowing how to decode a textbook. That&#39;s a shame."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "So I can diagnose the problem a little more specifically in math."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a really cool problem. I like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about defining steepness and slope"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "using a ski lift."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "But what you have here is actually four separate layers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m curious which of you can see the four separate layers"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "and, particularly, how when they&#39;re compressed together"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "and presented to the student all at once,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "how that creates this impatient problem solving."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll define them here: You have the visual."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "You also have the mathematical structure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "talking about grids, measurements, labels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "points, axes, that sort of thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "You have substeps, which all lead to what we really want to talk about:"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "which section is the steepest."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "So I hope you can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "I really hope you can see how what we&#39;re doing here"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "is taking a compelling question, a compelling answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;re paving a smooth, straight path"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "from one to the other"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "and congratulating our students for how well"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "they can step over the small cracks in the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s all we&#39;re doing here."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "So I want to put to you that if we can separate these in a different way"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "and build them up with students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "we can have everything we&#39;re looking for in terms of patient problem solving."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "So right here I start with the visual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "and I immediately ask the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "Which section is the steepest?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "And this starts conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "because the visual is created in such a way where you can defend two answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 339260.0,
      "text": "So you get people arguing against each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "friend versus friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "in pairs, journaling, whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "And then eventually we realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s getting annoying to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "the skier in the lower left-hand side of the screen"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "or the skier just above the mid line."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "And we realize how great would it be"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "if we just had some A, B, C and D labels"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "to talk about them more easily."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "And then as we start to define what does steepness mean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "we realize it would be nice to have some measurements"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 365260.0,
      "text": "to really narrow it down, specifically what that means."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 365260.0,
      "end_time": 367260.0,
      "text": "And then and only then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 367260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "we throw down that mathematical structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "The math serves the conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "the conversation doesn&#39;t serve the math."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 376260.0,
      "text": "And at that point, I&#39;ll put it to you that nine out of 10 classes"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 376260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "are good to go on the whole slope, steepness thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "But if you need to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "your students can then develop those substeps together."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "Do you guys see how this, right here, compared to that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 388260.0,
      "text": "which one creates that patient problem solving, that math reasoning?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 391260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been obvious in my practice, to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll yield the floor here for a second to Einstein,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "who, I believe, has paid his dues."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "He talked about the formulation of a problem being so incredibly important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "and yet in my practice, in the U.S. here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "we just give problems to students;"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t involve them in the formulation of the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "So 90 percent of what I do"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "with my five hours of prep time per week"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "is to take fairly compelling elements"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "of problems like this from my textbook"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 415260.0,
      "end_time": 418260.0,
      "text": "and rebuild them in a way that supports math reasoning and patient problem solving."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 418260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s how it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "I like this question. It&#39;s about a water tank."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "The question is: How long will it take you to fill it up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "First things first, we eliminate all the substeps."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 428260.0,
      "text": "Students have to develop those,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 430260.0,
      "text": "they have to formulate those."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 430260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "And then notice that all the information written on there is stuff you&#39;ll need."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 435260.0,
      "text": "None of it&#39;s a distractor, so we lose that."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 435260.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "Students need to decide, \"All right, well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 437260.0,
      "end_time": 439260.0,
      "text": "does the height matter? Does the side of it matter?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "Does the color of the valve matter? What matters here?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "Such an underrepresented question in math curriculum."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 447260.0,
      "text": "So now we have a water tank."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 447260.0,
      "end_time": 449260.0,
      "text": "How long will it take you to fill it up? And that&#39;s it."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 449260.0,
      "end_time": 451260.0,
      "text": "And because this is the 21st century"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 451260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "and we would love to talk about the real world on its own terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "not in terms of line art or clip art"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "that you so often see in textbooks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "we go out and we take a picture of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "So now we have the real deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 465260.0,
      "text": "How long will it take it to fill it up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 465260.0,
      "end_time": 467260.0,
      "text": "And then even better is we take a video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 470260.0,
      "text": "a video of someone filling it up."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 470260.0,
      "end_time": 472260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s filling up slowly, agonizingly slowly."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 472260.0,
      "end_time": 474260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s tedious."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 474260.0,
      "end_time": 476260.0,
      "text": "Students are looking at their watches, rolling their eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 476260.0,
      "end_time": 479260.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re all wondering at some point or another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 482260.0,
      "text": "\"Man, how long is it going to take to fill up?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 482260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 487260.0,
      "end_time": 490260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how you know you&#39;ve baited the hook, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 494260.0,
      "text": "And that question, off this right here, is really fun for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 494260.0,
      "end_time": 496260.0,
      "text": "because, like the intro,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 496260.0,
      "end_time": 499260.0,
      "text": "I teach kids -- because of my inexperience --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 499260.0,
      "end_time": 501260.0,
      "text": "I teach the kids that are the most remedial, all right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 501260.0,
      "end_time": 504260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve got kids who will not join a conversation about math"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 504260.0,
      "end_time": 506260.0,
      "text": "because someone else has the formula;"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 506260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "someone else knows how to work the formula better than me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 511260.0,
      "text": "so I won&#39;t talk about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 511260.0,
      "end_time": 514260.0,
      "text": "But here, every student is on a level playing field of intuition."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 514260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "Everyone&#39;s filled something up with water before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 520260.0,
      "text": "so I get kids answering the question, \"How long will it take?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 520260.0,
      "end_time": 523260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got kids who are mathematically and conversationally intimidated"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 523260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "joining the conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 528260.0,
      "text": "We put names on the board, attach them to guesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 528260.0,
      "end_time": 530260.0,
      "text": "and kids have bought in here."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 530260.0,
      "end_time": 532260.0,
      "text": "And then we follow the process I&#39;ve described."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 532260.0,
      "end_time": 534260.0,
      "text": "And the best part here, or one of the better parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 534260.0,
      "end_time": 536260.0,
      "text": "is that we don&#39;t get our answer from the answer key"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 536260.0,
      "end_time": 538260.0,
      "text": "in the back of the teacher&#39;s edition."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 538260.0,
      "end_time": 541260.0,
      "text": "We, instead, just watch the end of the movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 541260.0,
      "end_time": 543260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 543260.0,
      "end_time": 545260.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s terrifying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 545260.0,
      "end_time": 547260.0,
      "text": "because the theoretical models that always work out"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 547260.0,
      "end_time": 549260.0,
      "text": "in the answer key in the back of a teacher&#39;s edition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 549260.0,
      "end_time": 551260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s great, but"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 551260.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s scary to talk about sources of error"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 553260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "when the theoretical does not match up with the practical."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 557260.0,
      "text": "But those conversations have been so valuable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 559260.0,
      "text": "among the most valuable."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 561260.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m here to report some really fun games"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 561260.0,
      "end_time": 563260.0,
      "text": "with students who come pre-installed"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 563260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "with these viruses day one of the class."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 568260.0,
      "text": "These are the kids who now, one semester in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 568260.0,
      "end_time": 570260.0,
      "text": "I can put something on the board,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 570260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "totally new, totally foreign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 574260.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ll have a conversation about it for three or four minutes more"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 574260.0,
      "end_time": 576260.0,
      "text": "than they would have at the start of the year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 576260.0,
      "end_time": 578260.0,
      "text": "which is just so fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 578260.0,
      "end_time": 581260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re no longer averse to word problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 581260.0,
      "end_time": 584260.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;ve redefined what a word problem is."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 584260.0,
      "end_time": 586260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re no longer intimidated by math,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 586260.0,
      "end_time": 588260.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re slowly redefining what math is."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 588260.0,
      "end_time": 590260.0,
      "text": "This has been a lot of fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 590260.0,
      "end_time": 593260.0,
      "text": "I encourage math teachers I talk to to use multimedia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 593260.0,
      "end_time": 595260.0,
      "text": "because it brings the real world into your classroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 595260.0,
      "end_time": 597260.0,
      "text": "in high resolution and full color;"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 597260.0,
      "end_time": 600260.0,
      "text": "to encourage student intuition for that level playing field;"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 600260.0,
      "end_time": 602260.0,
      "text": "to ask the shortest question you possibly can"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 602260.0,
      "end_time": 605260.0,
      "text": "and let those more specific questions come out in conversation;"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 605260.0,
      "end_time": 607260.0,
      "text": "to let students build the problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 607260.0,
      "end_time": 609260.0,
      "text": "because Einstein said so;"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 609260.0,
      "end_time": 612260.0,
      "text": "and to finally, in total, just be less helpful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 612260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "because the textbook is helping you in all the wrong ways:"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 617260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s buying you out of your obligation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 617260.0,
      "end_time": 620260.0,
      "text": "for patient problem solving and math reasoning, to be less helpful."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 620260.0,
      "end_time": 623260.0,
      "text": "And why this is an amazing time to be a math teacher right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 623260.0,
      "end_time": 625260.0,
      "text": "is because we have the tools to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 625260.0,
      "end_time": 627260.0,
      "text": "this high-quality curriculum in our front pocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 627260.0,
      "end_time": 629260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s ubiquitous and fairly cheap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 629260.0,
      "end_time": 631260.0,
      "text": "and the tools to distribute it"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 631260.0,
      "end_time": 633260.0,
      "text": "freely under open licenses"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 633260.0,
      "end_time": 636260.0,
      "text": "has also never been cheaper or more ubiquitous."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 636260.0,
      "end_time": 638260.0,
      "text": "I put a video series on my blog not so long ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 638260.0,
      "end_time": 641260.0,
      "text": "and it got 6,000 views in two weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 641260.0,
      "end_time": 644260.0,
      "text": "I get emails still from teachers in countries I&#39;ve never visited"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 644260.0,
      "end_time": 647260.0,
      "text": "saying, \"Wow, yeah. We had a good conversation about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 647260.0,
      "end_time": 650260.0,
      "text": "Oh, and by the way, here&#39;s how I made your stuff better,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 650260.0,
      "end_time": 652260.0,
      "text": "which, wow."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 652260.0,
      "end_time": 654260.0,
      "text": "I put this problem on my blog recently:"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 654260.0,
      "end_time": 656260.0,
      "text": "In a grocery store, which line do you get into,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 656260.0,
      "end_time": 658260.0,
      "text": "the one that has one cart and 19 items"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 658260.0,
      "end_time": 661260.0,
      "text": "or the line with four carts and three, five, two and one items."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 661260.0,
      "end_time": 664260.0,
      "text": "And the linear modeling involved in that was some good stuff for my classroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 664260.0,
      "end_time": 667260.0,
      "text": "but it eventually got me on \"Good Morning America\" a few weeks later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 667260.0,
      "end_time": 669260.0,
      "text": "which is just bizarre, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 669260.0,
      "end_time": 671260.0,
      "text": "And from all of this, I can only conclude"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 671260.0,
      "end_time": 673260.0,
      "text": "that people, not just students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 673260.0,
      "end_time": 675260.0,
      "text": "are really hungry for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 675260.0,
      "end_time": 677260.0,
      "text": "Math makes sense of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 677260.0,
      "end_time": 679260.0,
      "text": "Math is the vocabulary"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 679260.0,
      "end_time": 681260.0,
      "text": "for your own intuition."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 681260.0,
      "end_time": 684260.0,
      "text": "So I just really encourage you, whatever your stake is in education --"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 684260.0,
      "end_time": 687260.0,
      "text": "whether you&#39;re a student, parent, teacher, policy maker, whatever --"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 687260.0,
      "end_time": 690260.0,
      "text": "insist on better math curriculum."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 690260.0,
      "end_time": 693260.0,
      "text": "We need more patient problem solvers. Thank you. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}